Package: irtpar
Type: Package
Title: Estimate Bayesian IRT Models in Parallel
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-01-21
Authors@R: person("Fridolin", "Linder", email = "fridolin.linder@gmail.com", 
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Who to complain to <fridolin.linder@gmail.com>
Description: This packages allows the estimation of IRT models in parallel. It 
  is based on the algorithms described in Neiswanger et al. 2014.  
